Image->YoloV8-FGDET(ROI cropped)->MobileNetV3L->BBoxes(locality and class of object/bb on image)
                                ->LightCap->Caption(relation between objects/description of image)
                                
YoloV8-FGDET:
- Input: Image
- Output: multiple ROI(bboxes whre objects are detected)

MobileNetV3L:
- Input: ROI cropped from YoloV8-FGDET
- Output: BBoxes (locality and class of object/bounding box on image)

LightCap:
- Input: ROI cropped from YoloV8-FGDET
- Output: Caption (relation between objects/description of image)